Create Cluster
POST /api/clusters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Name": "Computer Science",
  "Description": "Courses related to computer science and programming"
}

Get All Clusters
GET /api/clusters

Get Cluster by ID
GET /api/clusters/5

Update Cluster
PUT /api/clusters/5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Name": "Computer Science & IT",
  "Description": "Courses related to computer science, programming, and information technology"
}